name: Gremplin's Vibe Bag
description: I bought some Versace perfumes for my cousins. The lady was nice and she handed me this Versace Parfum Bag as a gift. I always thought of flippin' a jacket for Gremplin and yet it seems the story of the origins of this bag seems much more fitting.

name: Cozomo's '1-2-3-to-da-4' Coat
description: What up Cozomo! Lovely to know you vibe with us in Swampville, Cuz!.
